52
00:03:07,328 --> 00:03:10,144
♪Until hair gets white,
still can't fathom♪

53
00:03:10,144 --> 00:03:12,352
♪Fate♪

54
00:03:13,472 --> 00:03:14,688
♪Where flowers fall♪

55
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:15,960
For you.

56
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:17,280
Well...

57
00:03:17,440 --> 00:03:18,240
This...

58
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:19,560
What is this?

59
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,600
It's you.

60
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,080
Doesn't look like you?

61
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:23,960
Me?

62
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:27,840
Yes.

63
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:31,000
That's more like it.

64
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,960
You shaped it so well.

65
00:03:36,480 --> 00:03:38,496
♪For a single pot of tea♪

66
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:41,960
Zhifeng.

67
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,360
It's getting late.

68
00:03:44,640 --> 00:03:45,760
Go back to sleep.

69
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:48,960
"Late"?

70
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,720
You again?

71
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:50,560
Zhifeng.

72
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:51,920
Your mask.

73
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:53,720
It's your mask.

74
00:03:58,200 --> 00:03:59,000
Your Majesty.

75
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:01,640
This is the list
of jinshi scholars who passed

76
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:02,760
