♪Stars and galaxies♪

194
00:10:16,704 --> 00:10:22,176
♪Time stretches long since your goodbye♪

195
00:10:55,273 --> 00:10:57,595
♪The wind drifts alone and free♪

196
00:10:59,201 --> 00:11:02,249
♪Through seasons, none asks of me♪

197
00:11:04,297 --> 00:11:07,120
♪Spring fades, and autumn wails♪

198
00:11:08,361 --> 00:11:11,868
♪Only the waning moon
lights my solitude♪

199
00:11:13,641 --> 00:11:16,295
