200
00:11:17,710 --> 00:11:21,362
♪On a cold night,
a swan's shadow flashes by♪

201
00:11:22,825 --> 00:11:24,553
♪You're deeply devoted♪

202
00:11:25,156 --> 00:11:29,385
♪Yet spring wind betrayed your heart♪

203
00:11:30,921 --> 00:11:34,505
♪I miss you so much♪

204
00:11:34,505 --> 00:11:35,657
♪I never forget you♪

205
00:11:36,233 --> 00:11:39,529
♪A brief period of love-sickness♪

206
00:11:40,201 --> 00:11:43,049
♪You won my heart over♪

207
00:11:43,049 --> 00:11:45,428
♪Why did we first meet♪

208
00:11:45,428 --> 00:11:49,289
♪Seeking spring's song
and night whispers♪

209
00:11:49,289 --> 00:11:52,329
♪Long autumn comes,
and wild geese southward fly♪

210
00:11:52,329 --> 00:11:55,211
♪The azure clouds know my name♪

211
00:11:55,211 --> 00:11:58,633
♪I remember you, and you understand me♪

212
00:11:58,633 --> 00:12:01,481
♪Watching the sun set♪

213
00:12:01,593 --> 00:12:04,457
♪Autumn departs, and beauty fades away♪

214
